description.excerpt: ganslate is a PyTorch framework which aims to make GAN image-to-image translation more accessible to both beginner and advanced project with:
Extensibility for other datasets or architectures
A range of generator and discriminator architectures
Simple and extensible GAN image-to-image translation framework. Supports natural and medical images.

long_title.excerpt: `ganslate` - a simple and extensible GAN image-to-image translation framework

excerpt.body:
First release of ganslate package!

WIP: Documentation.

Features:

- 2D and 3D support
- Mixed precision
- Distributed training
- Tensorboard and Weights&Biases logging
- Natural and medical image support
- A range of generator and discriminator architectures
excerpt.name: Initial public release
